quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  42,16,"∆Āeen wee√Īiroo…ďe e diina Allah kan, …ďaawo ka ja…ďaneede, hujja ma…ď…ďe on ko mehre, tikkere no fawii e ma…ď…ďe, hino woodani …ďe kadi lepte ca…ótu…óe."
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri deftere nden goonga, e manndakke …óen. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara darnga ngal ko ko …ďadii?"
  42,18,"∆Āeya …ďe gooŇč…óinaani ngal …ďeen, hi…ďe he√Īoringal; gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen kan, ko …ďe hulu fii maggal, e hoore hi…ďe felliti won'de ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee won…ďe yeddondireede …ďen fii Darngal, ko pellet, …ďe ngonii e ndeer majjere wo…ó…óunde."
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jiyaa…ďe makko …ďen. Homo arsike on mo o muuyani. Ko KaŇčko woni Doolnu…óo, pool…óo On."
  42,20,"Kala taw…óo ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men …ďeydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi taw…óo ko jayru ndun aduna o yi…ói, Min ngokkay mo …óum, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) ge…óal."
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaa…ói hino woodani …ďe, sar'inan…ói …ďe e diina kan, ko ko Allah duŇčaaki fii mum? Si wonaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde ma…ď…ďe], √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Īu…ďe …ďen, lepte muus…óe."
  42,22,"A yi'at too√Ī…ďe …ďen hino huli e ko …ďe fggitii kon, …óum le ko yantay…óum e ma…ď…ďe. GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hi…ďe e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, kala ko …ďe faaletee. Ko …óuum tigiri, woni …ďural mawnungal ngal."